text: My Market Kitchen is an Australian cooking television series which debuted on Network Ten on 22 August 2016, currently hosted by Ben O'Donoghue. It was previously hosted by Emma Dean and Lynton Tapp from 2016 to 2018, then Elena Duggan and Khanh Ong for the 2019 series. ==References== == External links == *My Market Kitchen HQ at Instagram *My Market Kitchen TV *My Market Kitchen - About Us Category:Network 10 original programming Category:Australian cooking television series Category:2016 Australian television series debuts
